title: S16 Ep28: Expedition Bigfoot: Shocking Evidence with Dr. Mireya Mayor
itunes:title: Expedition Bigfoot: Shocking Evidence with Dr. Mireya Mayor
description:
Darkness Radio presents Expedition Bigfoot: Shocking Evidence with Dr. Mireya Mayor

Expedition Bigfoot is an amazing series now wrapping up it's successful 2nd season and a shock that surprised the cast and crew. Dr. Mayor returns to discuss new findings, new research and what the new findings mean.  

What does this all mean? Did they find Bigfoot? “Expedition Bigfoot” is currently streaming on discovery+. The series finale, “New Discoveries,” featuring the newly found eDNA evidence premieres on Sunday, March 28!

Get her book here: https://amzn.to/3t6rMwW

Visit her here: www.mireyamayor.com
